<hymn_number>20</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka gitloh ziekin van Lal cha thiengtho,
 Lei ah a hung a;
 * Khawvela mihiem min a zik lai un,
 Bethlehem bawng In sungah a siel ui,
 Ka hinna dingin (2) D.S.

[V2]
 2. Mi tin a dingin Hukdampa Lalpa,
 Nausen in a pieng;
 * Van mipiten kipah la a hun sau,
 Chungnung pena Pathien lopi pen hen;&quot;
 Ti'n a hun gen ui (2) D.S.

[V3]
 3. Aw A min chu -Mak, Lemguotpa Lalpa.
 Chamna Lal ahi;
 * Chamna hung leng hen khawvel chung ahin,.
 Khawsak michingte'n le a hun zui ui,
 A gam tawp puona (2) D.S.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Hinna Dingin</title>
</song>